front.title: •There Is Another
front.gametext: Plays on Your Destiny unless Leia or Luke has been deployed this game (even as a captive). [Death Star II] Luke and We're The Bait are lost. Opponent's Objective and [Death Star II] Effects target Leia instead of Luke. Force loss from Take Your Father's Place is -1.
front.lore: Princess Leia Organa. Alderaanian senator. Targeted by Vader for capture and interrogation. The Datk Lord of the Sith wanted her alive.
